<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Root.Access — Portfolio & Blog</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Root.Access - Portfolio and Blog  of Jackstar, a full-stack developer building modern web experiences.">
    <meta name="author" content="Jackstar">
    <!-- global core styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/root.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/index.css') }}">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-pb1a8fR2IG23QMGYBk8zQ7C0r4kOG55G4+7RThd7GxVbxmYFZHzqLTXW2dEVxErbqD0kKcl00Kd6cTDyXv4qOQ==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link rel="shortcut icon" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='assets/images/logos/LogoBrand.png') }}" type="image/png">
</head>
<body>
    {% include "snippets/navbar.jinja-html" %}
    <main>
        <section class="hero-section">
            <div class="container hero-container">
                <div class="hero-text">
                    <span class="badge">404: Bugs not found.</span>
                    <h1>
                        Serious About <span class="text-gradient">Code</span> 
                        <br>
                        Less About <span class="text-gradient">Me</span>  
                    </h1>
                    <p>I’m a Python developer with a strong focus on back-end, but I also have a side interest in front-end development. While HTML, CSS, and JS weren't exactly part of my original plan, I've picked them up along the way - and surprisingly, they tend to (mostly) work when I need them to.</p>
                    <div class="hero-actions">
                        <a href="/projects" class="btn-primary">Explore Projects</a>
                        <a href="/contact" class="btn-outline">Say Hello</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="hero-3d-wrapper">
                    <div class="hero-3d-card" id="tilt-card">
                        <div class="card-content">
                            <i class="fa-solid fa-terminal"></i>
                            <div class="line"></div>
                            <div class="line short"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="about-section">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-label">01. Identity</div>
                <div class="about-grid">
                    <div class="about-info">
                        <h2>
                            Hey, I'm Jackstar 
                            <br>
                            Austrian by birth, coder by choice
                        </h2>
                        <p>
                            I'm based in Austria, where I spend my time building things - some of which actually work. In my free time, I enjoy diving into personal projects, experimenting with new ideas, and exploring the more creative side of tech. Whether it's coding just for the fun of it or working on professional projects
                        </p>
                        <a href="/about" class="text-link">Learn more about my me →</a>
                    </div>
                    <div class="about-stats">
                        <div class="stat-box">
                            <span class="number">10+</span>
                            <span class="label">Projects</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="stat-box">
                            <span class="number" id="years-of-experience">Many</span>
                            <span class="label">Years of Experience</span>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="projects-preview">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-header">
                    <div>
                        <div class="section-label">02. Portfolio</div>
                        <h2>My Latest Projects & Selected Work</h2>
                    </div>
                    <a href="/projects" class="btn-secondary">View Gallery</a>
                </div>
                <div class="project-grid">
                    {% if preview_projects %}
                        {% for project in preview_projects %}
                            {% include "snippets/project_card.jinja-html" %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% else %}
                        <p class="no-results">No projects to display at the moment.</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="blog-preview">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="section-label">03. Insights</div>
                <div class="section-header">
                    <h2>Latest from the Blog</h2>
                    <a href="/blog" class="btn-secondary">Browse all articles</a>
                </div>
                <div class="blog-list">
                    {% if preview_blogs %}
                        {% for blog in preview_blogs %}
                            {% include "snippets/blog_card.jinja-html" %}
                        {% endfor %}
                    {% else %}
                        <p class="no-results">No recent articles available.</p>
                    {% endif %}
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    {% include "snippets/footer.jinja-html" %}
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/global.js') }}"></script>
    <script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/index.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>